        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.0</title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                    <h2>Tibok 1.0 - Initial Release</h2>
                    <p>The first public release of Tibok markdown editor with all essential features:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Clean, distraction-free markdown editor with live preview</li>
                        <li>35+ slash commands for markdown formatting and structure</li>
                        <li>Integrated Git workflow (stage, commit, push, pull, branch management)</li>
                        <li>Direct WordPress publishing support</li>
                        <li>Plugin system for extensibility</li>
                        <li>Math/LaTeX rendering with bundled KaTeX</li>
                        <li>Workspace and file management with smart filtering</li>
                        <li>Dark/light mode with system preference support</li>
                        <li>Customizable editor fonts, line height, and preview width</li>
                        <li>Keyboard shortcuts for all major functions</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h3>System Requirements</h3>
                    <p>macOS 14.0 (Sonoma) or later, Apple Silicon (ARM64)</p>
                ]]>
            </description>
            <pubDate>Fri, 19 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
